              "free_text": [
                " 7Be areal density.",
                "Energy scale of dymanitron determined from",
                " 19F(p,alpha gamma) thick target yields at 224.4,",
                " 340.46, and 872.11 keV resonances.",
                "7Be areal density measured",
                " 1) relative to yield of 7Li(d,p)8Li reaction at",
                "    0.77-MeV resonance.",
                " 2) using yield of 478-keV gamas in Ge(Li) detector",
                "    whose efficiency found using calibrated gamma",
                "    sources of 54Mn, 133Ba, and 137Cs.",
                "Solid angle of detector determined by comparing alpha",
                " particle yield with 7Li(d,p)8Li->8Be*->2alpha in the",
                " near geometry (2 mm target-collimator distance) to",
                " that in a far geometry (target-collimator distance",
                " 22.2mm)."
              ]
            }
